data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is located in the highly desirable, gated community of River Bridge.  The bright, eat-in kitchen has been updated, offering a modern space for your culinary adventures. The bathrooms have also been refreshed, providing a contemporary touch. Enjoy the tranquility of the gated surroundings and the soothing views of the lake. This home is an invitation to experience comfort and simplicity in a well kept, active, all ages community. Close to restaurants, shopping, and parks, this home has all you're looking for and more.
